description: Welcome to 392 West 2nd Street—a handsome 4-bed, 2.5 bath home with 2,000 sq ft of modern living space. Constructed from the ground up in 2012, it offers a blend of contemporary style and traditional charm, making it a standout family home in vibrant South Boston. Step inside to discover a light-filled, open-concept layout where the kitchen flows seamlessly into the living areas, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Step outside to your private balcony for grilling and relaxing.This home features a secluded heated driveway shared by association members, where the owner’s children safely ride scooters and play.  Parking is a breeze with an attached private 3 car garage with direct access. The location is unbeatable, with proximity to Southie’s best restaurants, enhancing the urban lifestyle this home provides. Embrace the opportunity to live in a lively area while enjoying the comforts of a well-designed, thoughtfully appointed residence that lives like a single family home.
